      <li>One-page or micro-site: <strong>$800–$2,000</strong></li>
      <li>5–8 page small business site: <strong>$1,500–$6,000</strong></li>
      <li>Small eCommerce (&le;100 products): <strong>$5,000–$15,000+</strong></li>
      <li>Custom/complex builds: <strong>$10,000–$50,000+</strong></li>
      <li>Ongoing: hosting $25–$120+/mo, domain ~$25/yr, care plans vary</li>
    </ul>

